* ''Taraxacum glabra''<ref name=ITIS/>
* ''Taraxacum laevigatum'' (Willd.) DC.<ref name=ITIS/>  <!-- -- red-seed dandelion, rock dandelion, rock dandylion -->
* ''Taraxacum lecerum'' Greene<ref name=ITIS/>
* [[白花蒲公英|白花蒲公英]]（''Taraxacum leucanthum'' Ledeb.）<ref name="中国科学院">{{cite web|url=http://vbd.brim.ac.cn/consult/wzhbmdb/wzhbmdb.htm|title=物种编目数据库检索|publisher=[http://cbis.brim.ac.cn/ 中国生物多样性信息系统]|accessdate=2009-07-11|archive-date=2011-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110603121932/http://vbd.brim.ac.cn/consult/wzhbmdb/wzhbmdb.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>  
